---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Project Architecture & Design System">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-7xl">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="text-center mb-16">
      <div class="flex justify-center mb-6">
        <div class="badge badge-primary badge-lg p-4 text-lg">Design System</div>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Project Architecture</h1>
      <p class="text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
        This portfolio is built with modern web technologies to empower employers, reduce costs, and inspire creativity.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Framework Overview Section -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title text-2xl mb-4">Framework Integration</h2>
          <div class="prose max-w-none">
            <p>
              This portfolio project demonstrates the seamless integration of three powerful frameworks:
            </p>
            <ul>
              <li>
                <strong>Astro</strong> - The core framework providing exceptional performance through partial hydration and static site generation
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Tailwind CSS</strong> - Utility-first CSS framework for rapid UI development with minimal CSS overhead
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>DaisyUI</strong> - Component library built on Tailwind CSS that provides accessible, themeable components
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              Together, these technologies create a maintainable, performant, and visually appealing website that follows best practices.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Typography Showcase -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Typography System</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Typography Examples -->
        <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-xl">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title text-xl mb-4">Typography Examples</h3>
            <div class="prose max-w-none">
              <h1>Heading 1</h1>
              <h2>Heading 2</h2>
              <h3>Heading 3</h3>
              <h4>Heading 4</h4>
              <p>Regular paragraph text with <strong>bold text</strong> and <em>italic text</em> for emphasis.</p>
              <blockquote>
                Blockquotes are styled to stand out from the rest of the content, making them perfect for highlighting important information or quotes.
              </blockquote>
              <p>Code snippets like <code>const value = 'example';</code> are styled inline.</p>
              <pre><code class="language-js">// Code blocks are styled with proper formatting
function example() &#123;
  return "Hello, world!";
&#125;</code></pre>
              <ul>
                <li>Unordered list item 1</li>
                <li>Unordered list item 2</li>
                <li>Unordered list item 3</li>
              </ul>
              <ol>
                <li>Ordered list item 1</li>
                <li>Ordered list item 2</li>
                <li>Ordered list item 3</li>
              </ol>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Typography Implementation -->
        <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-xl">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title text-xl mb-4">Implementation Details</h3>
            <div class="prose max-w-none">
              <p>
                The typography system is implemented using the <a href="https://github.com/tailwindlabs/tailwindcss-typography" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Tailwind CSS Typography plugin</a>, which provides a set of prose classes to style text content.
              </p>
              <p>
                Key features of our typography implementation:
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li>Responsive text sizing across all device sizes</li>
                <li>Consistent spacing between text elements</li>
                <li>Theme-aware styling that adapts to light and dark modes</li>
                <li>Accessible color contrast ratios</li>
                <li>Custom font stack using Inter and Cal Sans</li>
              </ul>
              <p>
                To use the typography styles, simply add the <code>prose</code> class to a container element:
              </p>
              <pre><code class="language-html">&lt;div class="prose"&gt;
  &lt;h1&gt;Your content here&lt;/h1&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Styled automatically with proper spacing and hierarchy&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Component Showcase -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">DaisyUI Component System</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- Buttons -->
        <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-xl">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title text-xl mb-4">Buttons</h3>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <button class="btn">Default</button>
              <button class="btn btn-primary">Primary</button>
              <button class="btn btn-secondary">Secondary</button>
              <button class="btn btn-accent">Accent</button>
              <button class="btn btn-ghost">Ghost</button>
              <button class="btn btn-link">Link</button>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4">
              <p class="text-sm opacity-70">All buttons use DaisyUI's <code>btn</code> class with modifiers.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Cards -->
        <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-xl">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title text-xl mb-4">Cards</h3>
            <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-sm">
              <div class="card-body p-4">
                <h4 class="card-title text-lg">Card Title</h4>
                <p>Cards organize content into containers with consistent styling.</p>
                <div class="card-actions justify-end mt-2">
                  <button class="btn btn-sm btn-primary">Action</button>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4">
              <p class="text-sm opacity-70">Cards use DaisyUI's <code>card</code>, <code>card-body</code>, and <code>card-actions</code> classes.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Alerts -->
        <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-xl">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title text-xl mb-4">Alerts</h3>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <div class="alert alert-info">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="stroke-current shrink-0 w-6 h-6"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
                <span>Information message</span>
              </div>
              <div class="alert alert-success">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="stroke-current shrink-0 h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
                <span>Success message</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4">
              <p class="text-sm opacity-70">Alerts use DaisyUI's <code>alert</code> class with status modifiers.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Layout System -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Layout System</h2>
      
      <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title text-xl mb-4">Responsive Grid Layout</h3>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="bg-primary/20 p-4 rounded-lg text-center">Column 1</div>
            <div class="bg-primary/20 p-4 rounded-lg text-center">Column 2</div>
            <div class="bg-primary/20 p-4 rounded-lg text-center">Column 3</div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="prose max-w-none">
            <p>
              The layout system is built using Tailwind CSS's utility classes for flexbox and grid, following the guidelines from <a href="https://daisyui.com/docs/layout-and-typography/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">DaisyUI's layout documentation</a>.
            </p>
            <p>
              Key layout features include:
            </p>
            <ul>
              <li>Responsive grid system that adapts to different screen sizes</li>
              <li>Consistent spacing using Tailwind's spacing scale</li>
              <li>Container-based layout with appropriate max-widths</li>
              <li>Flexbox utilities for alignment and distribution</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              Example of a responsive grid implementation:
            </p>
            <pre><code class="language-html">&lt;div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4"&gt;
  &lt;div&gt;Column 1&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div&gt;Column 2&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div&gt;Column 3&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Framework Links -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Learn More About Our Stack</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- Astro -->
        <a href="/astrojs" class="card bg-base-200 hover:bg-base-300 transition-colors shadow-xl">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title text-xl">Astro</h3>
            <p>The web framework for content-driven websites with exceptional performance.</p>
            <div class="card-actions justify-end mt-4">
              <div class="badge badge-outline">Framework</div>
              <div class="badge badge-primary">Core</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
        
        <!-- Tailwind -->
        <a href="/tailwind" class="card bg-base-200 hover:bg-base-300 transition-colors shadow-xl">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title text-xl">Tailwind CSS</h3>
            <p>Utility-first CSS framework for rapid UI development with minimal overhead.</p>
            <div class="card-actions justify-end mt-4">
              <div class="badge badge-outline">Styling</div>
              <div class="badge badge-secondary">Utilities</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
        
        <!-- DaisyUI -->
        <a href="/daisyui" class="card bg-base-200 hover:bg-base-300 transition-colors shadow-xl">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title text-xl">DaisyUI</h3>
            <p>Component library for Tailwind CSS with themeable, accessible components.</p>
            <div class="card-actions justify-end mt-4">
              <div class="badge badge-outline">Components</div>
              <div class="badge badge-accent">UI</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Employer Benefits -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <div class="card bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/20 to-secondary/20 shadow-xl">
        <div class="card-body text-center">
          <h2 class="card-title text-2xl justify-center mb-4">Benefits for Employers</h2>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-6">
            <div class="card bg-base-100/50 backdrop-blur-sm shadow-md">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="card-title text-xl justify-center">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
                  </svg>
                  Empowerment
                </h3>
                <p>This architecture empowers your team with modern tools and practices that increase productivity and satisfaction.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card bg-base-100/50 backdrop-blur-sm shadow-md">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="card-title text-xl justify-center">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                  </svg>
                  Cost Reduction
                </h3>
                <p>Reduce development costs through component reuse, faster development cycles, and improved maintainability.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card bg-base-100/50 backdrop-blur-sm shadow-md">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="card-title text-xl justify-center">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
                  </svg>
                  Creativity
                </h3>
                <p>Inspire creativity by providing a flexible, component-based system that encourages innovation and experimentation.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <p class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            By adopting this architecture, your team can focus on solving business problems rather than reinventing the wheel, resulting in faster time-to-market and higher quality products.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
